summary: "Yang represents the sun, male and light colors. Yin represents the night, female and the dark colors. Both complement each other and it is not possible for one to exist without the other." The queen met her dark eyes with the shining eyes of the prince. Could she go on with her life without her own Yang? Could she just remain Yin? Was she really strong enough to resist both nature and her heart? Maybe love wasn't a weakness, it was time for Yin to merge with Yang.
